Package: tmjmenu
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         python3 (>= 3.10),
         python3-gi,
         python3-xlib,
         gir1.2-gtk-4.0,
         gir1.2-adw-1,
         x11-utils,
         xdotool
Recommends: tmjos-branding,
            gir1.2-gtk4layershell-1.0,
            libgtk4-layer-shell0
Description: TMJOs proprietary application menu + dock
 Replaces Plank dock and GNOME Activities Overview with two integrated
 components, both GTK4 + libadwaita native (same stack as TMJPad):
 .
   * tmjmenu — popup search launcher, opened by Super key
   * tmjdock — dock no painel INTERNO do laptop (eDP/LVDS/DSI) com
     anchor bottom-center via gtk4-layer-shell (Wayland nativo) ou
     X11 hints (XWayland/Xorg fallback). Detecção do monitor interno
     ignora qual está marcado como primary — sempre ancora no laptop.
 .
 gir1.2-gtk4layershell-1.0 + libgtk4-layer-shell0 são Recommends pra
 layer-shell Wayland; se ausentes, tmjdock cai pro fallback X11 sem
 quebrar.
